OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMost seeing
OL,6,Fclear spells overnight with
OL,7,Fintermittent areas of cloud. Winds
OL,8,Fbecoming light and often variable.
OL,9,FStaying mild overnight, but more
OL,10,Fcomfortable than recent nights.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FA bright start, though cloud
OL,13,Fbuilding throughout the morning. This
OL,14,Fbringing the odd shower by the
OL,15,Fafternoon but some sunny spells still
OL,16,Fbreaking through. Temperatures
OL,17,Fdropping for all.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
